Mr. Jones is a phenomenal person and advisor. Please take a minute to support him!

history.content:
Are you an EECS student or are an Engineering Physics student who has received helpful advice or support from ESS adviser Bryan Jones? Do you believe Bryan is deserving of an Outstanding Advisor Award?


Then support Bryan by sending an email to Elizabeth Wilcox (ewilcox@berkeley.edu) by this Wednesday, November 7 to describe the support you receive(d) from Bryan and how that has helped you. Please include Bryan’s name in the subject line.


For more information about the advising award, please visit https://advisingmatters.berkeley.edu/advising-awards. Bryan is nominated for the Outstanding Advisor and Mary Slakey Howell awards.


Thank you!
